{
  "stem": "27748.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't remember discussing it, talking about it with my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were basically two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first one I've already mentioned, around 1934.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the second one was the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Kristallnacht is a date that stands out in my mind because it was also my birthday night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The night of my birthday was the night of the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That is, I was born on November 10th and the-- the events took place on the 9th to the 10th, so I couldn't very well ignore it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But during the daytime on the 9th, suddenly a lot of cars came from outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were no-- nobody owned cars in my village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So cars came up and people came out who arrested all the Jewish men, including my brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My brother was then 17.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all the Jewish men were suddenly taken away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had heard about events that led up to Kristallnacht in terms that a German embassy official in France had been assassinated by a Jew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we knew there were things in the air, but we didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So during the daytime, all of a sudden all the Jewish men were arrested and we were terribly scared.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother and I-- my sister had already left for America and my brother had left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my mother and I went to the neighbor house and-- where there was the girl, Margot, and her mother, and we hid in the attic, in the evening, in their attic.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then during the night, we heard cars come up and people starting smashing buildings and smashing the front door of the place in the house where I lived, where I was hiding upstairs in the attic, and smashing everything.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
